What is the total amount each customer has payed us so far (Hint: QUICK-Stop has payed us 110.277,32)
Find the 10 top selling products (Hint: Top selling product is "CÃ´te de Blaye")
Create a view with total revenues per customer
Which UK Customers have payed us more than 1000 dollars (6 rows)
How much has each customer payed in total and how much in 1997. We want one result set with the following columns:

CustomerID
CompanyName
Country
Customer's total from all orders
Customer's total from 1997 orders
You can try this with views, subqueries or temporary tables. Try using [Order Subtotals] view that already exists in database. (91 rows, Customer "Centro comercial Moctezuma" has 100,80 total revenues and zero (0) revenues in 1997 )
